{"id":"44cb3e64-1ece-4679-b237-39d4b4b0c34d","type":"ScenarioReference","class":"Mythos","tokens":{"front":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-999,"description":"Draw another token. If you fail, resolve Micolash Ceverny's Patrol keyword."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. X is the number of resource tokens on the scenario reference card."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-2,"description":"-2. If you fail, shuffle the closest empty location back into the Nightmare of Mensis deck and replace it with an Empty Space from the top of your deck."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-3,"description":"-3. If you fail and there is a Forced effect on your location, resolve that effect as if your location was just put into play."}},"back":{"Cultist":{"modifier":-999,"description":"Draw another token and resolve Micolash Ceverny's Patrol keyword."},"Skull":{"modifier":-999,"description":"-X. X is one more than the number of resource tokens on the scenario reference card."},"Tablet":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. If you fail, shuffle the closest empty location back into the Nightmare of Mensis deck and replace it with an Empty Space from the top of your deck."},"Elder Thing":{"modifier":-4,"description":"-4. If there is a Forced effect on your location, resolve that effect as if your location was just put into play."}}},"TtsZoopGuid":"44cb3e64-1ece-4679-b237-39d4b4b0c34d"}
